### **H∆∞·ªõng d·∫´n s·ª≠ d·ª•ng**
1. **T·∫°o file `.bas`**:
   - L∆∞u ƒëo·∫°n m√£ v√†o **VBA Editor**, ch·ªçn module, nh·∫•p chu·ªôt ph·∫£i, ch·ªçn `Export File` v√† l∆∞u v·ªõi t√™n `ConsolidateFiles.bas`.

